Bafana Bafana goalkeeper Darren Keet is urging South Africans to #StayHomeSaveLives. President Cyril Ramaphosa declared a 21-day nationwide lockdown amid the rapid rise in the COVID-19 infection rates in the country. he has put in place new guidelines to only leave the house if absolutely essential. SA athletes say we all have a responsibility to help the World Health Organisation (WHO) to stop the spread of coronavirus. 